                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3604" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0553</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9970 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">90后打造的“网红”喜茶：要排队购买的新式茶饮</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The &quot;web celebrity&quot; HEYTEA created by a post-90: New teas that must be bought in line</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">傅利平，黄修齐</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">喜茶HEYTEA</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">喜茶；创业；商标权保护；社会化媒体营销；二手资料撰写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HEYTEA ; Entrepreneurship; Protection of trademark rights; Social media marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">茶饮是中国传统文化中重要的一部分，但却被现代年轻人所忽略，茶饮市场也一度处于消费断层阶段。喜茶作为新式茶饮的代表企业，一直致力于茶饮的年轻化与科技化，创造性地研发出芝士现泡茶工艺，打开了新的消费市场，让这一古老文化焕发出新的生命力，让饮茶成了一种年轻人的生活方式。作为起步于三线城市的草根品牌，喜茶一路摸爬滚打，最终成为消费者热捧的全民“网红”茶。本案例在回顾喜茶的诞生、成长、成熟、抓住行业风口和突破红海困境的基础上，深入剖析了喜茶在不同时期面临的主要问题及解决对策。通过喜茶的案例，我们可以发现创业机会识别和创业过程中资源、资本、团队的平衡是创业成功的关键；商标权保护是创新型企业保持竞争优势的重要选择；善于迎合消费者心理和利用社会化媒体营销是打开消费品市场的有力武器。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Tea drinking is an important part of Chinese traditional culture, but it is ignored by modern young people, and at one time, the tea market was in the stage of consumption fault. As a representative enterprise of new tea drinks, HEYTEA has been committed to making tea drinks younger and more scientific, creatively developing the cheese brewing tea process, opening up a new consumer market, giving new vitality to this ancient culture, and making tea drinking a way of life for young people. As a grassroots brand starting from a third-tier city, HEYTEA has been struggling all the way, eventually becoming a popular &quot;web celebrity&quot; tea among consumers. This case on the basis of reviewing the birth, growth, maturity of HEYTEA, and how HEYTEA grasps the industry and breaks through the red sea dilemma, makes an in-depth analysis of the main problems and solutions faced by HEYTEA in different periods. Through the case of HEYTEA, we can find that the identification of entrepreneurial opportunities and the balance of resources, capital and team in the process of entrepreneurship are the key to the success of entrepreneurship; Trademark right protection is an important choice for innovative enterprises to maintain their competitive advantages; Being good at catering to consumer psychology and utilizing social media marketing is a powerful weapon to open up the consumer goods market.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理学》、《市场营销学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业管理、市场营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
